Package: geometricMVE
Title: Parametric and semiparametric statistical estimation of multivariate extremes via a geometrical approach
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Jennifer", "Wadsworth", email="j.wadsworth@lancaster.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ryan", "Campbell",  email="Ryan.CAMPBELL@univ-cotedazur.fr", role = c("aut")),
    person("Jeongjin", "Lee",  email="j.lee58@lancaster.ac.uk", role = c("ctb")))
Description: Model fitting and diagnostic tools for the geometric approach to multivariate extremes.
              Includes parametric forms for gauge functions (Wadsworth and Campbell, 2024) and semi-parametric piecewise linear forms (Campbell and Wadsworth, 2025). Explicit forms for bivariate additive mixture gauges, discussed in Lee and Wadsworth (2025), are also included.
